Salt Water Pool Home with Large SPA. Upgrades galore! Whole House Generac Generator w/500 Gallon Underground Propane Tank - Whole House Water filtration - Solar Panels -Plantation Shutters - Security System - Furniture included with exceptions, Items Identified by BLUE TAPE Do Not Convey - Protected Bald Eagle Nesting Area across the street. "NO FLOODING" - Gutters & Screens Damaged by Hurricane IAN have been replaced. >ASSESSMENTS PAID< Call today for a Showing Appointment; You'll be glad you did!
